    "long_instructions": "## Generating Content Chat\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to turn your best brainstorming idea into real content for your product launch.\r\n\r\nFocus on producing something concrete that matches your role—like a name and slogan, a logo description, a commercial script, or a jingle.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Use AI Chat to develop your strongest idea into polished content. You might ask:\r\n    - What do I want AI to help me write, design, or describe? \r\n    - What should it sound, look, or feel like?\r\n    - What key details should it include?\r\n    - Are there examples or references I can provide to get better results?\r\n2. As you generate content, add it directly to your group slide deck in the section for your role (name + slogan, visuals, script, or jingle).\r\n3. Want better results? Use specific language in your prompt—like the tone you want, key phrases to include, or the audience you’re trying to reach.",
